title: Looking for some Casuals or Ranked friends
body:
Hi,
I'm from Europe and played mostly on the EUW Servers, but as I moved here to Australia I changed the Server. Would be nice to have some People to play sometimes under the week or weekend Ranked, Aram or whatever. :)

I don't care if somebody is Bronze 5 or Challenger, u can just add me under xSun WukonGx  if u want.

replies.body: Uh, I'm maining urgot at the moment so you dont have to add me but i'll send a request :){{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}}
